title: K-Lite Codec Pack 11.6.5 Mega_Fulandard_Basic Final Nov2015
description:
Seven7i Presents

K-Lite Codec Pack 11.6.5 Mega_Full_Standard_Basic 

November 6th 2015

K-Lite Codec Pack FullK-Lite: 
Codec Pack is a collection of components 
needed for audio and video playback in DirectShow 
players such as Windows Media Player, Media Center, 
and Media Player Classic. It contains everything you 
need to play all common audio and video file formats. 
It also provides additional functionality such a 
thumbnail generation in Explorer. The pack has 
a very advanced installer which is highly 
flexible and has unique problem solving capabilities. 

Changes in 11.6.5:
Updated MPC-HC to version 1.7.9.190
Updated LAV Filters to version 0.66-33-g4179e
Updated madVR to version 0.89.13
Updated MediaInfo Lite to version 0.7.79
Updated Icaros to version 3.0.0 rc3


Enjoy,
Seven7i :)
